      "the rust monster drops the item on the ground in its own space.</span><span class=\"hanging-indent\"><b>Rust</b> A rust monster’s antenna causes metal to rapidly rust and corrode. If it succeeds at an antenna Strike or Disarm attempt with its antenna",
